{"id":698308127,"lang":"typescript","lang_name":"TypeScript","time":"1 year, 5 months","timestamp":1652388317,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"244 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/698308127/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Palindrome Number","memory":"51.9 MB","code":"function isPalindrome(x: number): boolean {\n    //return parseInt(x.toString().split(\"\").reverse().join(\"\")) == x\n    let num = [];\n    if (x<0) return false\n    while(x>0) {\n        num.push(x%10);\n        x = (x-(x%10))/10;\n    }\n    for(let k=0; k <= num.length/2; k++) {\n        if(num[k] !== num[num.length-k-1]) {\n            return false\n        }\n    }\n    return true;\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"palindrome-number","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
